<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>the ring is jeweler made.  since platinum never trivials, there's always a <BR>
possibility of failure.  thus you have the high cost due to lost materials.<BR>
<BR>
same reason why all plat jewelry is expensive, basically :)<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
